REPO: eclipse-vertx/vert.x
PR #5478: Update the node selector implementation to handle ordering of select calls
Changed files (27): vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/ClusteredEventBus.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/DefaultNodeSelector.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/NodeSelector.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/Serializer.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/selector/Index.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/selector/NullRoundRobinSelector.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/selector/RoundRobinSelector.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/selector/SimpleRoundRobinSelector.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/selector/Weight.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/eventbus/impl/clustered/selector/WeightedRoundRobinSelector.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/impl/VertxBootstrapImpl.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/impl/VertxImpl.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/spi/cluster/ClusterManager.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/spi/cluster/ClusteredNode.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/spi/cluster/impl/DefaultNodeSelector.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/spi/cluster/impl/selector/SelectorEntry.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/io/vertx/core/spi/cluster/impl/selector/Selectors.java, vertx-core/src/main/java/module-info.java, vertx-core/src/test/java/io/vertx/test/fakecluster/FakeClusterManager.java, vertx-core/src/test/java/io/vertx/tests/cluster/DefaultNodeSelectorTest.java, vertx-core/src/test/java/io/vertx/tests/cluster/selector/SimpleRoundRobinSelectorTest.java, vertx-core/src/test/java/io/vertx/tests/cluster/selector/WeightedRoundRobinSelectorTest.java, vertx-core/src/test/java/io/vertx/tests/eventbus/ClusteredEventBusTest.java, vertx-core/src/test/java/io/vertx/tests/eventbus/CustomNodeSelectorTest.java, vertx-core/src/test/java/io/vertx/tests/eventbus/MessageQueueOnWorkerThreadTest.java
Diff (+696/-532):
PR DESCRIPTION:
Motivation:
    
The `DefaultNodeSelector` implementation relies on a promise to broadcast the resolution of an address to its waiters. Ordering is therefore implemented as a per Vert.x context construct prior selector resolution, ordering is achieved per vertx context and per address using a temporary queue.
    
Ordering is required because the node selector and the underlying cluster manager use a cached promise to resolve the multiple select calls which does not maintain ordering. Since we do control the node selector implementation, ordering can be achieved in the node selector itself, providing the ordering required that the cluster manager does not provide.
    
Changes:
    
Updated the node selector implementation to implement ordering.
    
A linked list of select result promises is kept in a concurrent map until the cluster manager response is obtained, when the promise resolves the result promise list is resolved in arrival order an the list of registration is cached with the round robin selector for new node selector requests.
    
As consequences ordering is implemented based on the order of node selector calls.


